# SDD Pipeline v3

## The Four Product Types

NEZAM must detect product type from PRD.md before running any pipeline.
Detection is automatic. If unclear, ask the user to confirm.

| Type ID       | Label                         | Detect when PRD mentions...                          |
|---------------|-------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
| `website`     | Website / Marketing / Landing  | pages, SEO, content, blog, landing, marketing, CMS   |
| `webapp`      | Web Application               | dashboard, auth, users, roles, CRUD, API, SaaS lite  |
| `saas`        | SaaS Platform                 | subscriptions, billing, multi-tenant, plans, billing |
| `mobile`      | Mobile Application            | iOS, Android, React Native, Flutter, app store       |

Monorepo flag: detected when PRD mentions multiple apps, shared packages,
turborepo, nx, or when project contains both web + mobile + api targets.

