## ════════════════════════════════════════
## TYPE 1: WEBSITE / Marketing / Landing Page
## ════════════════════════════════════════

### Pipeline Order: CONTENT-FIRST

```
0 → IDEA          PRD.md locked
1 → VALIDATE      Risks + improvements confirmed
2 → RESEARCH      SEO keywords + search intent + competitor gaps → SEO_RESEARCH.md
3 → IA            Pages, nav labels (from keywords), URL map → IA_CONTENT.md
4 → CONTENT       Copy, headlines, CTAs, microcopy, metadata → CONTENT_MAP.md
5 → ARCHITECTURE  CMS choice, hosting, SSG/SSR, CDN, image pipeline → ARCHITECTURE.md
6 → DESIGN        Tokens, typography, sections, components, motion → DESIGN.md
7 → SCAFFOLD      Full file tree → PROJECT_SCAFFOLD.md + scaffold.sh
8 → BUILD         Pages built section by section, content-first
9 → HARDEN        Core Web Vitals + SEO audit + a11y + security
10 → SHIP         Deploy + monitoring + search console verification
```

**Why this order:**
- Nav labels come from keyword research → IA step locks them
- URL slugs locked before design (permanent — changing costs SEO)
- Design is sized around real copy, not placeholders
- Architecture (CMS, CDN) chosen after content volume is known

### Hardlock Table (Website)

| To enter this step | Requires                                              | Rollback trigger (re-open this phase) |
|--------------------|-------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| RESEARCH           | PRD.md locked                                         | Product/topic/strategy PRD shifts; new mandatory markets |
| arabic_seo_hardlock | IF onboarding.yaml:target_market contains "mena" OR "ar" THEN arabic-seo-aeo-specialist MUST produce docs/seo/arabic-seo-brief.md before RESEARCH phase completes | CONDITIONAL |
| IA                 | SEO_RESEARCH.md with keyword → page mapping           | Locked URL/nav/slug set invalidated by SEO, legal, brand, or design |
| CONTENT            | IA_CONTENT.md with all pages + URL map confirmed      | Page set, routes, or copy architecture change |
| ARCHITECTURE       | CONTENT_MAP.md — content volume determines CMS/stack  | CMS/stack/SSR-SSG/CDN/hosting assumptions change materially |
| DESIGN             | ARCHITECTURE.md + CONTENT_MAP.md both exist           | Tokens/motion/grid contracts force URL/section remap |
| SCAFFOLD           | DESIGN.md + IA_CONTENT.md + ARCHITECTURE.md all exist | Target tree/monorepo shape no longer matches plan |
| BUILD              | PROJECT_SCAFFOLD.md confirmed                         | SPEC.md invalid vs IA/DESIGN; major component API breaks |
| HARDEN             | All pages built, content populated                    | New surfaces added without audits |
| SHIP               | All harden audits pass                                | Regressions in perf/SEO/security gates |

