## ════════════════════════════════════════
## TYPE 3: SAAS PLATFORM
## ════════════════════════════════════════

### Pipeline Order: ARCHITECTURE + BILLING-FIRST

```
0 → IDEA          PRD.md locked
1 → VALIDATE      Risks + improvements + market fit confirmed
2 → RESEARCH      Market research + ICP + pricing research → MARKET_RESEARCH.md
3 → ARCHITECTURE  Multi-tenancy model + billing + data model + API → ARCHITECTURE.md
4 → IA            App navigation, user flows, admin flows, onboarding → IA_CONTENT.md
5 → DESIGN        Design system + dashboard patterns + onboarding UI → DESIGN.md
6 → CONTENT       Marketing copy + in-app copy + email sequences → CONTENT_MAP.md
7 → SEO           Public pages keyword research → SEO_RESEARCH.md
8 → SCAFFOLD      Full file tree → PROJECT_SCAFFOLD.md + scaffold.sh
9 → BUILD         Slices: auth→billing→core feature→admin→public site
10 → HARDEN       Security + compliance + perf + a11y audit
11 → SHIP         Deploy + monitoring + billing live + error tracking
```

**Why this order:**
- Multi-tenancy architecture determines EVERYTHING: database schema, auth model, API design, data isolation
- Billing model must be locked before first line of code (changing billing mid-build is catastrophic)
- SaaS has two distinct UIs: the app (architecture-first) + the marketing site (content-first)
- SEO for public pages comes after architecture, because the tech stack affects rendering strategy (SSG vs SSR)

### Hardlock Table (SaaS)

| To enter this step | Requires                                                          | Rollback trigger (re-open this phase) |
|--------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| RESEARCH           | PRD.md locked                                                     | Pricing tier/ICP that changes tenancy or billing model |
| ARCHITECTURE       | Market research + pricing model confirmed in PRD                  | Multi-tenant isolation or billing primitives change materially |
| IA                 | ARCHITECTURE.md with multi-tenancy model + billing model locked   | Admin/app/onboarding IA no longer fits tenancy or billing |
| DESIGN             | IA_CONTENT.md with all flows (app + admin + onboarding)           | Dashboard/onboarding/token patterns invalidate IA flows |
| CONTENT            | DESIGN.md — need all screens to write all copy states             | Marketing/legal copy scope shifts product promises |
| SEO                | ARCHITECTURE.md — stack determines SSG/SSR rendering capability   | Public-marketing routing or rendering strategy changes |
| SCAFFOLD           | All planning docs (arch + design + IA + content + SEO) exist       | Workspace layout/package map no longer valid |
| BUILD              | PROJECT_SCAFFOLD.md confirmed                                     | Feature slices invalid vs billing/auth/tenant model |
| HARDEN             | All feature slices pass acceptance criteria                       | New compliance/regulatory surface without audit |
| SHIP               | All harden audits pass + billing tested end-to-end                | Billing regressions or production gate failures |

