## ════════════════════════════════════════
## TYPE 4: MOBILE APPLICATION
## ════════════════════════════════════════

### Pipeline Order: ARCHITECTURE + OFFLINE-FIRST

```
0 → IDEA          PRD.md locked
1 → VALIDATE      Risks + native capability requirements confirmed
2 → RESEARCH      Market research + App Store research + competitor apps
3 → ARCHITECTURE  Data model + offline strategy + push + native APIs → ARCHITECTURE.md
4 → IA            Screen map + navigation patterns + user flows → IA_CONTENT.md
5 → DESIGN        Design system: touch targets, gestures, safe areas → DESIGN.md
6 → CONTENT       In-app copy + push notification copy + onboarding → CONTENT_MAP.md
7 → SCAFFOLD      Full file tree → PROJECT_SCAFFOLD.md + scaffold.sh
8 → BUILD         Slices: navigation shell → auth → core screens → extras
9 → HARDEN        Performance + accessibility + offline testing + store checklist
10 → SHIP         App store submission + CI/CD + crash monitoring
```

**Why this order:**
- Offline strategy (sync model) determines the entire data architecture
- Navigation pattern (tab bar / stack / drawer) must be locked before design — changing it mid-build breaks everything
- Touch targets and safe areas are architectural constraints, not styling choices
- App Store requirements affect architecture (privacy manifest, entitlements, permissions)

### Hardlock Table (Mobile)

| To enter this step | Requires                                                          | Rollback trigger (re-open this phase) |
|--------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| RESEARCH           | PRD.md locked                                                     | Store/category or core capability pivot |
| ARCHITECTURE       | Platform confirmed (iOS / Android / RN / Flutter)                 | Offline/sync/push or native APIs change materially |
| IA                 | ARCHITECTURE.md with offline model + push strategy confirmed      | Navigation shell (tabs/stack/drawer) or flows invalidated |
| DESIGN             | IA_CONTENT.md with navigation pattern + screen map confirmed      | Touch/safe-area/motion/token rules break screen inventory |
| CONTENT            | DESIGN.md — need all screens to write all copy + push copy        | Permission/push/message taxonomy scope changes |
| SCAFFOLD           | ARCHITECTURE.md + DESIGN.md + IA_CONTENT.md all exist            | Repo/module layout diverges from plan |
| BUILD              | PROJECT_SCAFFOLD.md confirmed                                     | SPEC vs navigation/offline mismatch |
| HARDEN             | All screens built, offline tested on real device                  | New entitlement/privacy-critical path without QA |
| SHIP               | App store checklist complete + crash monitoring configured        | Submission blockers or monitoring gaps |

