## ════════════════════════════════════════
## MONOREPO / TURBOREPO SUPPORT
## ════════════════════════════════════════

### When to use Monorepo

Use Monorepo when the project has 2+ of these:
- A web app + a public marketing website
- A web app + a mobile app
- A shared design system / component library used in multiple apps
- A backend API used by multiple frontends
- Multiple SaaS tiers (e.g., customer-facing app + internal admin app)

### Monorepo Pipeline Addition

After Step 3 (ARCHITECTURE), insert:

```
3a → MONOREPO DESIGN  Define workspace packages, shared contracts,
                       dependency graph, build pipeline → MONOREPO.md
```

MONOREPO.md must define:
- Each package: name, type, consumers
- Shared packages: `packages/ui`, `packages/config`, `packages/types`, `packages/utils`
- App packages: `apps/web`, `apps/app`, `apps/mobile`, `apps/api`
- Build order and dependency graph
- Which packages are publishable vs internal

