### Monorepo Hardlock Addition

Before `/DEVELOP` on any app, confirm:
- `MONOREPO.md` exists and defines the package it belongs to
- Shared packages (`ui`, `types`, `utils`) have their own SPEC.md entries
- The app's specific scaffold section is confirmed in `PROJECT_SCAFFOLD.md`

