## Feature Slice Protocol (all types — Step BUILD)

Each feature before coding begins:
1. Spec: `docs/plan/0N-build/<feature-slug>/SPEC.md`
2. Spec includes: acceptance criteria, data model changes, API contract, UI states, edge cases
3. Agent assigned before work starts
4. Slice reviewed by PM-01 before merge: `go` / `no-go` / `replan`

No feature slice may begin without a complete SPEC.md.
This is a non-bypass hardlock enforced by PM-01.
